### Health Check
GET http://localhost:5000/health

### Home
GET http://localhost:5000/

### Disease Detection
POST http://localhost:5000/api/disease/analyze
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="test_face.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test_images/test_face.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### Skincare Analysis
POST http://localhost:5000/api/skincare/analyze
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="test_face.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./test_images/test_face.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="questionnaire"

{"concerns": ["Acne", "Dark Circles"], "sleep_hours": "5-6 hours", "water_intake": "3-5 glasses", "stress_level": "Moderate"}
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### Chatbot - Stored Answer
POST http://localhost:5000/api/chatbot/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "how to treat acne",
  "skin_type": "Oily"
}

### Chatbot - AI Generated
POST http://localhost:5000/api/chatbot/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "is coconut oil good for my face",
  "skin_type": "Dry"
}